OL,3,CWho are the MSPs being sworn at
OL,4,CHolyrood?
OL,6,FNew MSPs have been sworn in at the
OL,7,FScottish Parliament.
OL,9,FScotland has a total of 129 MSPs being
OL,10,Fformally sworn in lined up for the
OL,11,Foath of office, pledging their "true
OL,12,Fallegiance" to King Charles and his
OL,13,Fsuccessors, including 11 MSPs elected
OL,14,Fto represent the ITV Border region
OL,15,Facross the South of Scotland.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
