OL,3,CWho are the MSPs being sworn at
OL,4,CHolyrood?
OL,6,FThey include constituency MSPs
OL,7,FScottish Conservatives Finlay Carson,
OL,8,FCraig Hoy and Rachael Hamilton; Calum
OL,9,FKerr for the SNP, and list MSPs Carol
OL,10,FMochan and Joe Fagan for Scottish
OL,11,FLabour; Senga Beresford, David
OL,12,FKirkwood and Jamie Langan for Reform
OL,13,FUK; Laura Moodie for the Scottish
OL,14,FGreens; and Duncan Dunlop for the
OL,15,FScottish Liberal Democrats.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
