OL,3,CWho are the MSPs being sworn at
OL,4,CHolyrood?
OL,6,FOutside Holyrood, a small group of
OL,7,Fcampaigners from the group Stand Up to
OL,8,FRacism Scotland gathered to protest
OL,9,Fagainst Reform. However, by the time
OL,10,Fthey had arrived the MSPs they were
OL,11,Ftargeting had already entered the
OL,12,Fbuilding.
OL,14,FThe leaders of the main political
OL,15,Fparties were first up, with the SNP's
OL,16,FJohn Swinney taking the opportunity to
OL,17,Fdeclare his "primary loyalty" to the
OL,18,F"people of Scotland".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
