CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778850694
OL,3,CWho are the MSPs being sworn at
OL,4,CHolyrood?
OL,6,FWith both Reform UK and Scottish
OL,7,FLabour having 17 MSPs, alphabetical
OL,8,Forder was used to determine who went
OL,9,Fnext. Lord Offord took his oath,
OL,10,Ffollowed by Anas Sarwar.
OL,12,FAfter the party leaders had taken
OL,13,Ftheir turn, the rest of the MSPs,
OL,14,Fincluding the ITV Border region's
OL,15,Fmembers, took the oath or affirmation.
OL,17,FMSPs will conduct a secret ballot to
OL,18,Felect this session's Presiding Officer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
